-Yeah. All right.

1124
01:17:58,655 --> 01:18:01,886
I didn't even get a chance to talk to him.

1125
01:18:02,058 --> 01:18:05,516
That crazy goddamn bastard.

1126
01:18:06,062 --> 01:18:09,054
What a waste.
What the hell was he thinking?

1127
01:18:09,733 --> 01:18:11,564
Marty? I gotta set this up.

1128
01:18:11,735 --> 01:18:13,259
Go. Go.

1129
01:18:14,003 --> 01:18:15,334
You okay?

1130
01:18:16,072 --> 01:18:17,835
Yeah, I'm fine.

1131
01:18:19,109 --> 01:18:21,168
Come on, let's get you a drink.

1132
01:18:24,013 --> 01:18:28,245
