Like, did I push him too hard?

1133
01:18:28,418 --> 01:18:29,646
Not a chance.

1134
01:18:29,819 --> 01:18:31,616
I just couldn't get through to him.

1135
01:18:31,788 --> 01:18:34,951
What, you scared him to death?
Come on. The man was a bull.

1136
01:18:35,425 --> 01:18:39,054
-Never happened.
-Why does he fold, then? Why does he...?

1137
01:18:41,097 --> 01:18:42,962
It's gotta be an accident.

1138
01:18:43,133 --> 01:18:44,691
