1139
01:18:44,868 --> 01:18:47,837
He couldn't piss without leaving a memo.
Has to be an accident.

1140
01:18:48,004 --> 01:18:50,268
I don't get that.
I don't understand that either.

1141
01:18:50,440 --> 01:18:52,670
One minute he's gonna
take on the whole world...

1142
01:18:52,842 --> 01:18:55,868
