01:19:23,740 --> 01:19:25,401
You can say it.

1150
01:19:27,944 --> 01:19:29,844
We caught a lucky break.

1151
01:19:32,849 --> 01:19:35,147
We did, didn't we?

1152
01:19:39,856 --> 01:19:43,292
