1153
01:19:43,459 --> 01:19:45,188
-They accepted?
-In principle.

1154
01:19:45,361 --> 01:19:48,194
Don Jeffries wants us
on the phone in half an hour.

1155
01:19:48,364 --> 01:19:51,265
I tried to explain about Arthur,
but they're short on sympathy.

1156
01:19:51,434 --> 01:19:53,334
Wait a minute. U/North is settling?

1157
01:19:53,503 --> 01:19:57,564
They see a window. They wanna try.
It's their show. What are we gonna do?

1158
01:19:59,309 --> 01:20:02,437
You did what you could, Michael.
We all did.

1159
01:20:03,847 --> 01:20:05,178
It's....

1160
01:20:05,348 --> 01:20:07,009
It's what we got.

1161
01:20:08,151 --> 01:20:10,984
-You need a ride?
-No, thanks, I'm fine.

1162
01:20:43,786 --> 01:20:44,775
Hello.

1163
01:20:44,954 --> 01:20:47,548
Hello. Hi. I'm looking for Anna Kysersun.

1164
01:20:47,724 --> 01:20:48,816
<i>Who is this?</i>

1165
01:20:48,992 --> 01:20:52,484
Michael Clayton. I'm an attorney in
New York. I got your number from Arthur.

1166
01:20:52,662 --> 01:20:55,529
<i>-You have got some nerve.</i>
-Excuse me?

1167
01:20:55,698 --> 01:20:59,498
