Is this him or you?

1305
01:34:19,902 --> 01:34:22,496
-If I'm wrong, I apologize.
-You're way the fuck wrong.

1306
01:34:22,671 --> 01:34:23,899
So there you go.

1307
01:34:24,073 --> 01:34:25,734
Enough. Okay? Everybody.

1308
01:34:26,608 --> 01:34:28,769
He's an asshole, but he knows it.

1309
01:34:29,178 --> 01:34:32,443
And you're on the record.
Okay? Everybody happy?

1310
01:34:33,082 --> 01:34:35,778
-Don Jeffries is here.
-We're on the way.

1311
01:34:36,585 --> 01:34:40,681
Call Bob Nast.
Just see if they need help with this thing.

1312
01:34:44,259 --> 01:34:45,624
You're welcome.

1313
01:35:38,514 --> 01:35:40,880
You said 1 2. This is 75.

1314
01:35:41,049 --> 01:35:43,210
Well, don't get too excited.
You want a drink?

1315
01:35:43,385 --> 01:35:45,250
No. I'm working.

1316
01:35:47,689 --> 01:35:51,216
So we're square, then. No bad blood.

1317
01:35:51,393 --> 01:35:53,088
You're just doing your job.

1318
01:35:53,262 --> 01:35:54,729
That's right.

1319
01:35:55,664 --> 01:35:57,393
Take it easy, Gabe.

1320
01:35:58,400 --> 01:35:59,765
Michael.

1321
01:36:11,513 --> 01:36:12,946
<i>Check.</i>

1322
01:36:14,783 --> 01:36:16,045
<i>Check.</i>

1323
01:36:16,385 --> 01:36:19,115
-Check.
-Half the pot. Two hundred.

1324
01:36:19,288 --> 01:36:20,585
Two hundred to go.

1325
01:36:57,960 --> 01:36:59,723
So, what happened with the bar?

1326
01:36:59,895 --> 01:37:01,920
You just had to be a rock star, huh?

1327
01:37:24,419 --> 01:37:27,183
What are you doing? You just got here.

1328
01:37:27,356 --> 01:37:29,290
Guy plays nine hands, walks away.

1329
01:37:29,458 --> 01:37:33,622
I scare you away? What did I do?
Did I scare you away?

1330
01:38:09,398 --> 01:38:10,456
Get out.

1331
01:38:11,833 --> 01:38:13,960
<i>Get out of the car now.</i>

1332
01:38:15,704 --> 01:38:16,693
-Walter?
<i>-Michael.</i>

1333
01:38:16,872 --> 01:38:19,067
<i>-Michael. Thank God you're there.</i>
-Yeah.

1334
01:38:23,478 --> 01:38:25,412
You have eight...

1335
01:38:26,315 --> 01:38:29,045
<i>...six, five...</i>

1336
01:38:29,217 --> 01:38:31,549
<i>...four, three....</i>

1337
01:38:31,720 --> 01:38:33,347
<i>Get out of the car.</i>

1338
01:38:36,792 --> 01:38:39,818
-Tell him to stay off the phone.
<i>-All right. But you're on it?</i>

1339
01:38:40,429 --> 01:38:41,862
Am I clean?

1340
01:38:42,030 --> 01:38:43,258
Just keep walking.

1341
01:38:43,432 --> 01:38:45,662
You copy. Am I clean?

1342
01:38:45,867 --> 01:38:48,859
Just keep moving.
He's walking to the car.

1343
01:38:49,404 --> 01:38:52,965
<i>--to let him know you're on the way.</i>
<i>I'll get back to you with the details.</i>

1344
01:38:53,141 --> 01:38:55,575
<i>-Just give me two minutes.</i>
-I'll be in the car.

1345
01:38:59,281 --> 01:39:02,717
<i>I didn't finish. It's in, but I don't know.</i>

1346
01:39:30,879 --> 01:39:34,440
It's loose. I got a pulse.
He's up there somewhere, but....

1347
01:39:36,218 --> 01:39:38,152
Let's find a way to boost the signal.

1348
01:39:45,727 --> 01:39:48,924
-I don't know what Walter promised you--
-A miracle worker!

1349
01:39:49,097 --> 01:39:52,328
That's Walter on the phone,
20 minutes ago. Direct quote, okay?

1350
01:39:52,501 --> 01:39:54,332
"I'm sending you a miracle worker."

1351
01:39:54,503 --> 01:39:56,164
-Well, he misspoke.
-About what?

1352
01:39:56,338 --> 01:39:59,865
About the fact that you're the firm's fixer?
Or that you're any good at it?

1353
01:40:05,647 --> 01:40:07,581
We're up. Just got a signal.

1354
01:40:31,440 --> 01:40:33,806
There's nothing back this way.
What's he doing?

1355
01:40:33,975 --> 01:40:35,169
