1381
01:45:30,638 --> 01:45:33,163
-Yeah, yeah. They closed U/North.
-No. Michael Clayton.

1382
01:45:33,608 --> 01:45:34,666
What?

1383
01:45:34,843 --> 01:45:37,744
Car bomb. Upstate. This morning.
