1430
01:49:00,682 --> 01:49:02,013
I'm calling Marty.

1431
01:49:02,183 --> 01:49:04,549
Good. Good. Do it.
That's a great place to start.

1432
01:49:04,719 --> 01:49:07,517
Let's find out who told him
Arthur was calling Anna Kysersun.

1433
01:49:07,689 --> 01:49:09,520
Let's find out who tapped those phones.

1434
01:49:09,691 --> 01:49:13,491
This memorandum, even if it's authentic,
which I doubt, I highly doubt--

1435
01:49:13,661 --> 01:49:17,097
-I know what you did to Arthur.
-It's protected. It belongs to U/North.

1436
01:49:17,265 --> 01:49:20,029
-I know you killed him.
-It's attorney-client privilege.

1437
01:49:20,201 --> 01:49:23,864
See, now, that's just not
the way to go here, Karen.

1438
01:49:24,038 --> 01:49:26,734
For such a smart person,
you really are lost, aren't you?

1439
01:49:26,908 --> 01:49:28,239
This conversation is over.

1440
01:49:28,409 --> 01:49:31,845
I'm not the guy that you kill.
I'm the guy that you buy.

1441
01:49:32,013 --> 01:49:34,538
Are you so fucking blind
you don't even see what I am?

1442
01:49:34,716 --> 01:49:38,208
I'm the easiest part of your whole
goddamn problem and you're gonna kill me?

1443
01:49:38,519 --> 01:49:41,647
Don't you know who I am?
I'm a fixer. I'm a bagman.

1444
01:49:41,823 --> 01:49:45,224
I do everything from shoplifting housewives
to bent congressmen...

1445
01:49:45,393 --> 01:49:47,293
...and you're gonna kill me?

1446
01:49:48,229 --> 01:49:51,062
What do you need, Karen? Lay it on me.

1447
01:49:51,232 --> 01:49:54,929
You want a carry permit? You want
a heads-up on an insider-trading subpoena?

1448
01:49:55,103 --> 01:49:58,937
I sold out Arthur for 80 grand
and a contract and you're gonna kill me?

1449
01:50:00,441 --> 01:50:01,874
What do you want?

1450
01:50:02,043 --> 01:50:03,567
What do I want?

1451
01:50:03,745 --> 01:50:05,337
I want more.

1452
01:50:05,847 --> 01:50:07,610
I want out.

1453
01:50:07,782 --> 01:50:10,410
And with this, I want everything.

1454
01:50:12,186 --> 01:50:13,414
Is there a number?

1455
01:50:13,588 --> 01:50:15,180
Ten is a number.

1456
01:50:15,356 --> 01:50:17,381
Ten? Ten what?

1457
01:50:19,427 --> 01:50:20,917
Ten million?

1458
01:50:21,095 --> 01:50:24,531
Where do you think I'm gonna get
1 0 million dollars?

1459
01:50:25,099 --> 01:50:26,999
You know what's great about this?

1460
01:50:27,168 --> 01:50:29,466
Did you read it to the end?
You see who signed it?

1461
01:50:30,038 --> 01:50:31,938
Let's go in and ask Don Jeffries...

1462
01:50:32,106 --> 01:50:35,098
...if he wants to pass the hat
for a worthy cause.

1463
01:50:36,944 --> 01:50:39,344
This would have to be
a longer conversation...

1464
01:50:39,514 --> 01:50:41,641
...and would have to take place
somewhere else.

1465
01:50:41,816 --> 01:50:43,306
Where? My car?

1466
01:50:44,886 --> 01:50:45,910
All right.

1467
01:50:47,088 --> 01:50:50,114
I'm gonna make it easy. Let's make it 5.

1468
01:50:50,291 --> 01:50:52,088
Five and I'll forget about Arthur.

1469
01:50:54,462 --> 01:50:59,229
Five is easier. Yeah, 5 is something
that we could talk about.

1470
01:50:59,400 --> 01:51:03,131
Good. And then the other 5 is
to forget about the 468 people...

1471
01:51:03,304 --> 01:51:05,397
...that you knocked off
with your weed killer.

1472
01:51:05,573 --> 01:51:07,939
Let me finish up this meeting.
I'll talk to Don--

1473
01:51:08,109 --> 01:51:10,703
Do I look like I'm negotiating?!

1474
01:51:10,878 --> 01:51:12,209
Karen?

1475
01:51:12,914 --> 01:51:14,779
-One second.
-Everything okay?

1476
01:51:16,150 --> 01:51:17,139
Yes.

1477
01:51:18,152 --> 01:51:21,952
Ten million dollars. Bank of my choosing.
Offshore. lmmediately.

1478
01:51:22,123 --> 01:51:23,249
-Yes.
-Say it!

1479
01:51:23,424 --> 01:51:27,292
Ten million dollars, your account,
the moment this meeting is through.

1480
01:51:27,462 --> 01:51:29,760
-Karen! Everyone's waiting.
-I'm coming, Don.

1481
01:51:30,798 --> 01:51:32,163
You have a deal.

1482
01:51:32,734 --> 01:51:33,996
You're so fucked.

1483
01:51:34,335 --> 01:51:35,666
